## Sass Variables **Scope**

<!-- slide -->

```scss
.example { $columns: 2; }
.nested-class { /* $columns == undefined */ }

@media (min-width: 30em) {
  .example { $columns: 6; }
  .nested-class { /* $columns == undefined */ }
}
```

<!-- slide -->

## CSS Variables **Inherit**

<!-- slide -->

```scss
.example { --columns: 2; }
.nested-class { /* var(--columns) == 2 */ }

@media (min-width: 30em) {
  .example { --columns: 6; }
  .nested-class { /* var(--columns) == 6 */ }
}
```

<!-- slide -->

## Inherit Everywhere:

```scss
