## Single **Source of Truth**

```scss
body {
  grid-template-areas:
      'header               header'           auto
      'nav                  main'             1fr
      'footer               footer'           auto
    / minmax(14em, auto)    minmax(0, 1fr);
}
```

<!-- slide -->

```scss
h1 { grid-area: header; }
nav { grid-area: nav; }
main { grid-area: main; }
footer { grid-area: footer; }
```

